snippet.textDisplay:
My light and love is Jesus Christ. There are many roads to God (we all stand before Him in judgment)..there is only one road to heaven, and that road is Jesus.
Jesus said I am the Way the Truth and the Life. No man comes to the father, but through me.
Eternal life is a free gift from God. We don't have to do anything but accept it and believe the good news.
First the bad news...We are all sinners in need of a savior. Because God is Holy He cannot tolerate sin. Sin must be punished. The punishment for sin is death. The good news Jesus came to earth (though He was God) took on flesh, dwelt among us. So He could die in our place and take our punishment. He did this on the cross. He rose again on the third day. He is alive forever more. He is sitting on the throne in heaven, and will be coming again.
The nano second you believe this, you are saved and sealed until the day of redemption. Nothing can separate you from God's love. You become born again..and can NOT become unborn. No power in heaven, on earth or in hell (including ourselves) can cause us to lose our salvation. Jesus lived a perfect sinless life. But he became sin on the cross, so that those who believe are now the righteousness of God. Every single sin past, present and future is covered by His blood. We can NOT lose our salvation. Even though we are still human and still sin. When we go to heaven God will take away our sin nature.
